    "title": "DMRCs Sh. Anuj Dayal Received Lifetime Achievement Award",
    "slug": "dmrcs-sh-anuj-dayal-received-lifetime-achievement-award",
    "excerpt": "DMRCs Sh. Anuj Dayal Received Lifetime Achievement Award",
    "content": "<header class=\"entry-header \">\n<h1 class=\"entry-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">DMRC&rsquo;s Sh. Anuj Dayal Received Lifetime Achievement Award</h1>\n<div class=\"entry-meta\">By <span class=\"posted-by vcard author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"> <a class=\"url fn n\" title=\"View all posts by Admin\" itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https://blogs.digitallynext.com/author/admin/\" rel=\"author\"> <span class=\"author-name\" itemprop=\"name\"> Admin </span> </a> </span> / <span class=\"published\" itemprop=\"datePublished\"> April 24, 2023 </span></div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"entry-content clear\" itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>New Delhi:&nbsp;</strong>Sh. Anuj Dayal, the Principal Executive Director of Delhi Metro Rail Corporation (DMRC), was honored with the prestigious Lifetime Achievement Award for his outstanding contribution to Corporate Communication &amp; Public Relations (PR) on National PR Day.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The award was conferred by the esteemed Press Club of India, Public Relations Society, Delhi, and Public Sector PR Forum in recognition of Sh. Dayal&rsquo;s remarkable achievements and contributions to the field of corporate communication and PR.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sh. Anuj Dayal has been an integral part of DMRC since its inception and has played a key role in establishing it as one of the most successful and efficient metro rail systems in the world.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To Read More Click Here :</span> <a href=\"https://www.psuconnect.in/amppage/news/dmrc-anuj-dayal-received-lifetime-achievement-award/37343/\">https://www.psuconnect.in/amppage/news/dmrc-anuj-dayal-received-lifetime-achievement-award/37343/</a></p>\n</div>",
