    "content": "<h2 class=\"eael-entry-title\"><a class=\"eael-grid-post-link\" title=\"PR and media professionals celebrate National Public Relations Day in association with the Press Club of India\" href=\"https://blogs.digitallynext.com/2023/04/27/pr-and-media-professionals-celebrate-national-public-relations-day-in-association-with-the-press-club-of-india/\">PR and media professionals celebrate National Public Relations Day in association with the Press Club of India</a></h2>",
